Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:21.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:35.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:57.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:10.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:14.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:23.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:27.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于进入大学联考的考季
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过居然报考这么多所大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有精神值得赞许
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考不上的还是考不上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤暗沈粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻头也干干的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌头也缺乏光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体状况不太好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少在这里胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是第二看好 今天要考的N大说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不可能了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赌全部都考不上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在看不出来 有哪一所他一定能考上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#04 响子紧张万分?五代考试中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有东西忘了带?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都带齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准考证带了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,当然有带罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天考的是N大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,我的安全牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是K大的准考证吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找死啊你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天就这样 接下来真令人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你偏心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么关心那个重考生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪小的或许也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱上那个重考生了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在胡说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员关心房客是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果五代今年又落榜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家也有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员真的生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(五代,请加油喔)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天惨败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜…拜托,还没放榜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考不上的啦,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天考不上,还有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱枪扫射总会扫中的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样一路落榜下去吧 我赚爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本不是在鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不是因为听了 朱美说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的大学入学考试连续惨败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没考的学校 也没剩下几所了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你午饭吃了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代不晓得考得还顺利吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生经常摸你的屁股吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太 请不要开这种恶质的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我看你的屁股蛮不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定可以生很多 健康的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等一下拿茶点去你那里坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下,一之濑太太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一大堆喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个医生喔,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男生长得很帅吧 听说是K大毕业的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢吗? 想不到你还蛮挑的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,这个如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好拼一拼 剩下比较有希望的学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底喜欢 哪一类型的男人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去相一次亲有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有打算要结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么? 你已经到了适婚年龄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有喜欢的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 好像有,又好像没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有没有?快说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是你还没有下定决心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是 我还没做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他非常地爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把惣一郎的事说出来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么爱那个重考生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会提到五代呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听你这么说 总觉得他最吻合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你好像 老是很在意那个重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里在意他了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还大叫一声 啊!五代!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再说了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?她大喊我的名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还是放弃他比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙毫无前途可言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他再怎么好运 顶多也只能进二流大学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有一技之长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意志也薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪又比你小,根本靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要把他 说得这么一文不值吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考一次是很平常的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他待人亲切,是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人最重要的是内在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我明白了 那我就暂时先撤退罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以这样就回去 请听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我不会跟重考生说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了 怎么有你这种男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜,我干嘛脸红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样反而会被误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,怎么有你这种男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会在走廊偷听 女人之间的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的声音太大声了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想听也听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你需要贴在门板上听吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊!就是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不明白 管理员的用心良苦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要我明说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会这么辛苦地保密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大学联考的紧要关头 她不想让你分心动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个误会太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,我去上学罗,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的牙齿好脏喔,要刷刷牙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候才要走啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的学校你最有把握不是吗? 快要迟到罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辄,等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以再被误会下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,你看 那是典型的考生打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呆喔,一定是重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了恭喜你金榜题名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不嫌弃接受我的吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今年也完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T大前站,T大前站 电车马上就要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经写完了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个心胸狭窄的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天明明是他最重要的考试…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在可能正在考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了啦,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以管理员的身分 为五代加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外没有任何的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你相信我,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是什么关系啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上卖艺的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是打电话给卫生局比较好吧 这种事很难说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是另类的外遇吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是彩券中了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了庆祝本店开张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别举办血拼大相送
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻 五代怎么可能会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生,请不要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,我真的太在意他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也是身为管理员的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!你误会了啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我误会什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,进来进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店我很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不想在大白天就喝酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐哪里好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐桌子那里吧,那里比较舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么响子会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来大杯的啤酒 还有鱼肉丸跟烤鱿鱼两人份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生,你身体不舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其它的出口吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那里!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧,有心事的时候喝酒最好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有心事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意早上的事,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很单纯地 担心五代考试的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酒量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是管理员耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道管理员不可以关心房客吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,你还没付钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,我忘了香烟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他正在考下午的科目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一下洗手间吧 我们还要继续喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在这里干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为题目实在太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说这下死定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你中途跑出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都已经在这里吃饭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了!真的气死我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次考试,我会跟着你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直盯着你 不让你中途落跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,请等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行为明明就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能放着你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没,就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,她是你的谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦,因为她说她一定要跟来…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.34,0:22:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,虽然我问了很多次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的有说我要来陪考吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得非常肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑大婶可以作证
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,拜托你再对我说那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得今天一定会很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你的背包…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪头,大猪头 你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真像个不中用的弟弟 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学联考落榜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生跳楼自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该…该不会是五代…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:24:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回 ‘响子焦虑不安!五代离家出走’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,请快点回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你会考上的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:06.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:35.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:43.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}光只是眨个眼 就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:51.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:25:06.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}明明已经可以相爱 偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:18.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}我快要忍受不了 快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}真是痛苦的折磨

